summary: An Ordinance authorizing the Mayor and City Comptroller to issue Local Improvement Bonds for the improvement of East Spring Street, from Twenty-fifth Avenue to Thirty-second Avenue, et al., in the City of Seattle, by constructing concrete sidewalks under Ordinance No. 14963, creating Local Improvement District No. 1317 prescribing the rate of interest thereon and authorizing their delivery to the contractor constructing the improvement.
